<component type="desktop-application">
  <id>io.github.rahatzamancse.ProtonGameSaves</id>
  <name>Proton Game Saves Manager</name>
  <summary>Manage Proton game save files for Steam games</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      Proton Game Saves Manager is a modern GTK4 application that helps you manage save files
      for Steam games running through Proton compatibility layer. It provides an easy-to-use
      interface to browse, organize, and manage your game saves.
    </p>
    <p>Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Browse and manage Proton prefix folders</li>
      <li>Easily navigate to save file locations for each game</li>
      <li>Delete unwanted prefixes to free up space</li>
      <li>Configure Steam directory location</li>
      <li>Modern GTK4/libadwaita UI following GNOME design guidelines</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
